  "body": "<p>Just love what Kelly Purkey has done with the Noted Daybook, available online at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144259-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-noted-daybook-kit/\">Two Peas</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=Noted%20Daybook&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D60996%2Fnote%2Dnoted%2Dday%2Dbook%2FDetail\">Simon Says Stamp</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/868275bbb3f35465.jpg?v=1782532663\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0623cb5df5871913.jpg?v=1782532666\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And I am crazy about her washi tapes - the colors are perfect not only for this season, but anytime. I personally don't need any excuses to collect more of this sticky stuff. Keeping it simple and small these days seems like a theme I can work with. How about you?</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}